node.text: Yesterday at Aulani, a Disney Resort & Spa, cast members celebrated the 10th anniversary of the resort with a special ceremony that included characters, new music and more! Check out the replay of the ceremony now and read more about the event on the Disney Parks Blog (link in bio).

node.text: Actor Kumail Nanjiani (@kumailn), who stars as Kingo in the upcoming film “Eternals,” recently assembled with Iron Man during his first visit to #AvengersCampus at Disney California Adventure park! For more on his visit, check out the Disney Parks Blog (link in bio).
